      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CONSIGLIERE (2) won again in another strong performance after running them ragged to make it two in a row, scoring by 1.3 lengths (29.44) at this track over 520m. Recorded one of the quickest times on the card in scoring last start. In form and can go on with it. ACCREDITED (1) has been hard to follow lately, running fifth (29.54) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at Q Parklands. Expected to bounce back to best. SEE THIS (7) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (29.91) at this track behind Dazzle You in a Grade 5. Settled off speed and worked to the line nicely. The form from his last run stacks up well. Will give a great sight again. MAGICAL ANG (6) cannot be underestimated.",
